data.title: Shops, Restaurants, Apartments & More
data.meta_description: Live, Work, Shop, Dine & Play in North Hills Raleigh. Premier dining establishments, high-end boutiques, department stores, and cafés are all a few steps in any direction.
data.text:
Founded in 2007, Sweetgreen passionately believes that real food should be convenient and accessible to everyone. Every day, across its over 200 restaurants, its team members create delicious seasonal meals from fresh ingredients and produce that prioritizes organic, regenerative, and local sourcing.

Read More

Situated in the heart of North Hills, the new johnnie-O store will offer customers an immersive shopping experience, showcasing the brand’s signature collection of versatile clothing. The johnnie-O brand offers a diverse assortment of apparel and accessories for men and women who appreciate quality, comfort, and effortless style.

Read More

Carolyn is the NC based creative mind and designer behind Bofémme Jewelry. Bofémme started in 2017 and since then it has evolved to be a brand focused on quality and uniqueness, using materials locally and ethically sourced. Carolyn would describe her style as boheme + feminine which is where the name Bofémme originates from. Carolyn is completely self taught and finds inspiration from nature and her surroundings. Each piece is a true refection of herself and truly one of a kind.
